        "content": "type: search_result\ntitle: AI Events in Berlin | AI Tinkerers Meetups 2026\nurl: \"https://berlin.aitinkerers.org/\"\ndescription: \"AI Tinkerers Berlin is built for engineers, founders, researchers, product builders, and developers working on AI agents, multimodal and voice interfaces, RAG and knowledge systems, AI coding tools, workflow automation, evals, observability, ...\"\npage_age: 1 day ago\nprofile_name: AI Tinkerers\nmeta_url_favicon: \"https://imgs.search.brave.com/8rQOgpZvkbfYiu_iQVBQsFLv4GllctowCLUa_gDKfa8/rs:fit:32:32:1:0/g:ce/aHR0cDovL2Zhdmlj/b25zLnNlYXJjaC5i/cmF2ZS5jb20vaWNv/bnMvMTExOTMyMTEw/Njk1ZDNjNjkwNzMz/M2QzYWVlYTgyOTQ5/NzA5MTRiZDlmYjdk/NGIwN2UwMjg1N2Yw/NzFiNDg4ZS9iZXJs/aW4uYWl0aW5rZXJl/cnMub3JnLw\"\nthumbnail_src: \"https://imgs.search.brave.com/gbr6EjQEbUlKGaQrSHZEAReM72cv6Abm4JNPPfFOyZ8/rs:fit:200:200:1:0/g:ce/aHR0cHM6Ly9zbG9w/cHktam9lLWFwcC5p/bWdpeC5uZXQvYmxv/Z19pbWFnZXMvZDNj/aTl2MnotZzQtb1dF/Ry5wbmc\"\nthumbnail_original: \"https://sloppy-joe-app.imgix.net/blog_images/d3ci9v2z-g4-oWEG.png\"\nextra_snippets: \"A typical AI Tinkerers Berlin meetup runs about three hours with live demos from local builders, technical Q&A, and networking. Demos are expected to show real systems or code, not sales decks. The next event is AI Tinkerers Berlin - June 17, 2026 on June 17, 2026.|\\\"The formula is great: get a bunch of builders in the room to show off what they’d built and talk about it. Keep it up!\\\" April 1, 2025 | Staff Software Engineer AI Tinkerers Berlin - April 1st ... \\\"the kind of people coming to the event really inspires me. not normal crowd for a tech meetup in Berlin. Loved it.\\\" July 18, 2024 | Student Ollama & Friends coming to AI Tinkerers Berlin|AI Tinkerers Berlin hosted an in-person meetup for practitioners building with foundation models and generative AI, fostering technical exchange and sharing messy experiments, supported by Vercel, Langdock, Zed, and Everyday Intelligence. ... Experienced builders gathered in person for an intense evening focused on creating Conversational Agents, with support from sponsors ElevenLabs and Redis.|AI Tinkerers Berlin is built for engineers, founders, researchers, product builders, and developers working on AI agents, multimodal and voice interfaces, RAG and knowledge systems, AI coding tools, workflow automation, evals, observability, and production AI infrastructure. Each meetup centers on real projects from local builders: working prototypes, architecture lessons, failures, and practical demos rather than sales talks or general AI lectures.\"\nhash: 69096c116e79f03a\nembed_ref: berlin.aitinkerers.org-gKi\napp_id: web\nskill_id: search",
